  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Changes to This Policy Washingtonian com reserves the right to change this policy at any time Please check this page periodically for changes We will post a notice on this site if and when this policy changes to alert visitors that a new policy is in place Your continued use of our website following the posting of changes to our privacy policy will mean that you accept such changes Information collected prior to the time any change is posted will be used according to the policy and applicable laws in place at the time the information was collected</evidenceContent>
